AI-Resume-Analyzer/
│
├── backend/                        # All backend code (Flask + PyTorch)
│   ├── app.py                      # Flask API for real-time inference
│   ├── model.py                    # PyTorch deep learning model
│   ├── preprocess.py               # Text preprocessing & tokenization
│   ├── dataset.py                  # PyTorch dataset class
│   ├── utils.py                     # Helper functions (optional)
│   └── train_and_save.py           # Script to train and generate model_state.pth
│
├── frontend/                        # Web interface
│   ├── index.html                  # Resume input and results page
│   ├── style.css                   # Styling for aesthetic UI
│   └── script.js                   # JS to interact with Flask API
│
├── data/                            # Sample dataset for testing
│   └── sample_resumes.csv          # CSV with dummy resumes and multi-label skills
│
├── models/                          # Folder for storing trained model weights
│   └── model_state.pth             # Saved PyTorch model (generated by train_and_save.py)
│
├── Dockerfile                       # For containerized deployment
├── requirements.txt                 # Python dependencies
├── README.md                        # Polished, recruiter-friendly project description
└── .gitignore                       # Ignore venv, __pycache__, model weights if needed
